  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们今天要梳理一下零售优惠券系统的核心交互逻辑。我注意到这个系统里有几个关键角色：BARG代表议价模块，VFI是订单履约引擎，还有POL是政策制定单元。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "VFI",
        "POL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，BARG作为核心议价模块，我理解它应该处于比较中心的位置。那DEF这个零售POS节点和BARG之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DEF定义了45%这个关键阈值，这个阈值直接约束BARG的议价空间。所以DEF到BARG应该是一条定义关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEF",
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把DEF指向BARG的关系标注为\"defines '45%'\"了。另外我看到SOFT订单管理模块，它会影响议价过程对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SOFT",
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，SOFT通过影响库存可用性来间接影响bargaining。还有COMP这个POS组件，它会向BARG添加额外的约束条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SOFT",
        "COMP",
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加SOFT到BARG的\"affects bargaining\"，以及COMP到BARG的\"adds constraints\"。接下来GOV客户忠诚度模块呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SOFT",
        "COMP",
        "GOV",
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GOV比较特殊，它不直接连BARG，而是通过shifts boundaries去影响VFI。因为忠诚度规则的变动会改变履约引擎的边界条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GOV",
        "VFI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "清楚了。那DISC和VFI的关系是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DISC",
        "VFI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DISC是订单管理的折扣子模块，它会给VFI增加负载压力，所以是\"adds load\"的关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DISC",
        "VFI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的。现在BARG作为中心节点，它对外应该有不少输出吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "BARG非常关键，它有四条出边：重置DEF的规则、收紧COMP的审计、扩展SOFT的交易条款，以及设定GOV的集成条款。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "DEF",
        "COMP",
        "SOFT",
        "GOV"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "四条出边都已添加。我注意到ABF这个忠诚度数据模块还没连上，它和DEF的关系是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ABF",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ABF向DEF输送基础数据，是feeds data的关系。另外VFI和OUT之间也有联系，VFI的spillover demand会传导到OUT这个零售POS出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ABF",
        "DEF",
        "VFI",
        "OUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接ABF到DEF，以及VFI到OUT。DISC和OUT之间也有occupancy loop的循环关系对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ABF",
        "DEF",
        "VFI",
        "OUT",
        "DISC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，occupancy loop是个反馈环。还有OUT到POL的media pressure关系，以及POL到BARG的changes stance。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OUT",
        "POL",
        "BARG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。OUT还有一条crisis response直接回到BARG？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OUT",
        "BARG",
        "POL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，危机响应机制。另外POL和DEF之间还有一条虚线关系，标注为narrative，表示政策叙事层面的软性影响。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "POL",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "虚线narrative已添加。现在来看样式，BARG和VFI、POL、OUT应该是主要节点吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "VFI",
        "POL",
        "OUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，BARG、VFI、POL是primary类别，用浅黄底色配深棕边框。OUT作为outcome类别，用浅红底色。DEF、SOFT、COMP、GOV、DISC、ABF都是secondary，用浅蓝底色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "VFI",
        "POL",
        "OUT",
        "DEF",
        "SOFT",
        "COMP",
        "GOV",
        "DISC",
        "ABF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式类已定义。OUT还需要特别加粗边框，以及把它放进Retail_CouponSystem这个子图里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OUT",
        "O"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "子图O就是Retail_CouponSystem，但OUT既是子图内的节点，也是外部可见的端口。DEF虽然也是POS，但它放在子图外面作为定义源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OUT",
        "O",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，OUT在子图O内部，DEF在外部。子图O本身也用浅红底色和细边框区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "O",
        "OUT",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "检查一下，BARG到DEF的resets rules，和DEF到BARG的defines 45%，这两条会不会有歧义？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我理解这是双向但语义不同的关系：DEF先定义阈值，BARG在运行时可以重置规则，形成控制闭环。这样表达是准确的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个细节，VFI到OUT的spillover demand和DISC到OUT的occupancy loop，这两条都指向OUT，但一个是需求溢出，一个是占用循环，要区分开标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VFI",
        "DISC",
        "OUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "标注已确认区分。POL到DEF的虚线narrative是点划线样式，我也设置好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "POL",
        "DEF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 27,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整体结构没问题了。primary节点BARG、VFI、POL突出显示，secondary节点围绕支撑，OUT作为关键出口单独强调，子图O包裹整个系统边界。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BARG",
        "VFI",
        "POL",
        "OUT",
        "O"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 28,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已最终确认。所有节点关系、样式类别、子图结构都按您的要求完成了。这个图清晰展示了零售优惠券系统中议价模块BARG与履约引擎VFI、政策单元POL之间的核心交互，以及POS、订单管理、忠诚度等模块的支撑作用。",
      "elements_involved": [
